H0.text: Male reproductive system is the system that includes the penis, testes, and epididymis.

H1.text: Virus reproductive system is the system that includes the penis, testes, and epididymis.

H2.text: Plant reproductive system is the system in which the penis, testes, and epididymis are organs.

H3.text: The female reproductive system includes the penis, testes, and epididymis.

A4.text: The main male sex organs are the penis and the scrotum, which contains the testicles that produce semen and sperm

A5.text: The sperm that are produced in the seminiferous tubules flow into the epididymis
